Overview

This dashboard shows Breach Record overview related to the SpyCloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested breach records from SpyCloud.

It showcases the aggregate count of infected IP addresses, and infected email accounts. It presents the distribution of breach records across infected time and severity levels. The dashboard also offers a breakdown of hostnames and OS based on severity. Furthermore, it highlights the  top 10 targeted domains, top 10 hostnames by infected machine ID, the top 10 IPs associated with users, and the top 10 compromised countries. In addition to this, it illustrates the machine drilldown and the top 10 infected users. By default, it retrieves new records every day.
